Package ca.openosp.openo.integration.ebs.client.ng

Class EdtClientBuilderConfig

java.lang.Object
ca.openosp.openo.integration.ebs.client.ng.EdtClientBuilderConfig
public class EdtClientBuilderConfig extends Object
Configuration class for building the EDT client. This class encapsulates various settings required to authenticate and interact with the MCEDT service, such as user credentials, keystore information, and service-specific details.

Additional options like logging and MTOM (Message Transmission Optimization Mechanism) are also configurable.

An instance of this class can be passed to the EDt client builder to initialize and configure the service client appropriately.

  • Constructor Details

    • EdtClientBuilderConfig

      public EdtClientBuilderConfig()
      Creates a new instance of EdtClientBuilderConfig with a randomly generated audit ID. This audit ID uniquely identifies the client session in the logs, facilitating traceability and debugging. It is automatically assigned upon instantiation and remains constant throughout the client's lifecycle.
